 <br />\n新入行做得慢都畀人屌嘅話就炒老闆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6efe94203a15e8e65d956877d22d8babcf20138","tid":32701,"uid":44514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:34:19.000Z","msg":"做左幾個月<br />\n除左頭半個月編我上書外<br />\n其他時間都編我做counter<br />\n個人鐘意做counter <br />\n預著hea館可以玩手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f994b051f338457e6fb798f9335980f80ed367","tid":32701,"uid":44514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:37:42.000Z","msg":"不過真係幾悶下 人工低<br />\n最on9係間agent換左人 事假要兩星期前通知<br />\n最初想做係因為想體驗下<br />\n體驗夠差唔多打算轉工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a4c39e8c4f9248559154fc014aa3634d8b83c9e","tid":32701,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:38:28.000Z","msg":"係咪跟個肥佬做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ecc16507d8824427fbf159cd2a0390df7455dc1","tid":32701,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:44:29.000Z","msg":"人工低 佢會控制住你唔會爆鐘而有人工加<br />\n但係好hea 發呆放空玩手機轉筆係返工做最多<br />\n不過你要有對付d 痴線佬既心理準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"419b0514f6a662c943a47d5a0e8527702fd93b0e","tid":32701,"uid":43374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做細館好爽<br />\n<br />\n利申：做過某東區細館"},{"pid":"dc8698fabb5663439c2eaa304dc036af6fd99162","tid":32701,"uid":33539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T12:12:42.000Z","msg":"點入職<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8628ab6613b60feffc866cecd0e43c1f3174e1","tid":32701,"uid":62554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T12:15:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇你做邊區啦~中央某d層好hea</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁如果唔係中央呢？<img sr